Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.35,0:02:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四個小時前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.58,0:02:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 妳看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.35,0:02:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.58,0:02:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花島和木之下在閒聊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.45,0:02:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶 她們成為好朋友了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.52,0:02:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.82,0:02:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花島討厭那一型的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.03,0:02:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老覺得她們不曉得在打什麼鬼主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.73,0:02:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.90,0:02:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.70,0:02:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 花島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.04,0:02:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是妳們呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.27,0:02:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 被找碴了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.98,0:02:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說下次的學生報裡想寫以電波為題材的特輯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.18,0:02:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以來問我今天可不可以到我家採訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.75,0:02:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？做這樣的特輯要幹嘛呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.12,0:03:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道 但我老感覺得到其他電波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.96,0:03:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳答應她了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.10,0:03:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然 找上門來的電波我當然要應戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.07,0:03:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 這樣才對嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.17,0:03:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很煩但也挺有趣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.91,0:03:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打完工之後可以繞去妳家嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.44,0:03:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.78,0:03:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透也要來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.35,0:03:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天打工要打到晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.55,0:03:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.78,0:03:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.01,0:03:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的由希看起來格外光輝華麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.01,0:03:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道那是擔任下一屆會長所散發出來的威嚴之光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.45,0:04:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.62,0:04:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是王子的光輝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.45,0:04:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是由希天生散發出來的光輝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.66,0:04:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,素子學姊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.36,0:04:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"電波女家潛入大作戰"計劃成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.00,0:04:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 妳們做得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.07,0:04:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小南 一號、二號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.57,0:04:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.47,0:04:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼電波女沒有起疑心嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.34,0:04:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有 她輕易答應了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.48,0:04:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是一下子就點頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.32,0:04:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像騙人似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.38,0:04:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.19,0:04:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.75,0:04:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.26,0:04:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.49,0:04:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了祈求這麼偉大的計畫能順利成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.49,0:04:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位 露一手老招式吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.87,0:04:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"由希王子愛好會"副會長木之下南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.74,0:04:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.07,0:04:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會員一號 山岸美緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.78,0:04:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.04,0:05:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會員二號 後藤舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.51,0:05:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.22,0:05:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我是由希王子愛好會會長皆川素子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.19,0:05:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藉由我們四個人的力量 非讓這個計畫成功不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.86,0:05:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"驅除本田透"政策非成功不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.07,0:05:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"由希王子愛好會"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.47,0:05:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個存在於海原高中裡的草摩由希的崇拜會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.51,0:05:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而會員人數則占了海原高中女同學的半數以上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.32,0:05:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活動內容則是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.92,0:05:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由所有的會員一起來讚美、熱愛及守護降臨在本校的王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.96,0:05:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,講白一點就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.43,0:05:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別想一個人獨吞哦 爛貨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.07,0:05:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.00,0:06:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於愛好會的規定則要絕對嚴格服從
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.51,0:06:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一 不准偷王子的私人物品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.41,0:06:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一 不准偷王子的私人物品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.45,0:06:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二 不准潛入王子的住宅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.25,0:06:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二 不准潛入王子的住宅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.42,0:06:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三 和王子談話時需保持兩人以上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.03,0:06:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三 和王子談話時需保持兩人以上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.00,0:06:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四 稱呼王子時其稱呼方式如下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.10,0:06:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三年級稱由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.87,0:06:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.94,0:06:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二年級稱由希同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.67,0:06:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.84,0:06:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一年級稱草摩同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.77,0:06:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.38,0:06:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要違反這個規定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.04,0:06:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使不是會員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.75,0:06:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也會受到嚴格的懲罰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.52,0:06:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王子萬歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.85,0:06:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王子萬歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.32,0:06:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.76,0:06:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕能不原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.42,0:06:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然在快要畢業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.83,0:06:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才好不容易訂出的會員守則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.96,0:06:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和即將展開的各種會員活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.93,0:07:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻因本田透的各種行為而遭破壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.44,0:07:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本田透 那個女孩是魔女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.11,0:07:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們由希王子居然輕易被那個魔女給騙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.15,0:07:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果因這樣愛…愛上她的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.45,0:07:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我豈不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.42,0:07:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請別再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.85,0:07:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守護由希別讓魔女搶走是我們的職責啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.76,0:07:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.49,0:07:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣為何不找本田透 而要潛入電波女家中呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.83,0:07:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二號 妳問得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.40,0:07:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換句話說 魔女是受到擁有超大法力的魔王所庇護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.28,0:07:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以操縱毒電波的魔王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.11,0:07:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有被那個毒電波打到的人才會了解那種痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.09,0:07:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇～發生蝦咪代志啊！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.29,0:07:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會讓人昏睡一個禮拜而且腦海裡還有聲音死纏著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.26,0:07:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說了也沒有人相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.36,0:08:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以理解～小南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.53,0:08:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魚谷亞里莎雖然是太妹但還算是個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.63,0:08:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是有辦法對付得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.63,0:08:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過花島根本不是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.87,0:08:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已經超越人的極限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.20,0:08:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說得一點也沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.74,0:08:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想驅除魔女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.21,0:08:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須先驅除庇護她的魔王才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.68,0:08:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此這次的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.31,0:08:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"電波女家潛入大作戰"計畫絕不容許失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.82,0:08:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要找出魔王的弱點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.52,0:08:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主攻她的弱點讓她無法發出毒電波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.09,0:08:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做也是為了保護由希那顆清純的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.66,0:08:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.57,0:08:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這邊轉彎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.64,0:08:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花島同學不是搭電車上學的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.55,0:09:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位 絕不可以害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.55,0:09:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要強勢 要用強勢的態度挑戰魔王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.19,0:09:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.19,0:09:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花島同學的家會是哪種感覺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.01,0:09:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 萬一真的是那種地方該如何是好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.84,0:09:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候大家就拔腿開溜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.15,0:09:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.55,0:09:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.46,0:09:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有夠平常的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.72,0:09:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我得提醒一下各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.96,0:09:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個屋子最好別說出自己的真名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.70,0:09:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.93,0:09:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.00,0:09:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛死了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.80,0:09:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,素子學姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.04,0:09:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 1.2 1.2 …
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.92,0:10:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.49,0:10:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.59,0:10:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有鋼琴 真棒呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.36,0:10:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.30,0:10:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面也很普通啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.40,0:10:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不許掉以輕心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.25,0:10:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有這個月曆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.21,0:10:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.62,0:10:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.68,0:10:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡有賣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.95,0:10:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是車站前常關著沒開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.95,0:10:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長井嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.79,0:10:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.29,0:10:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個挺不錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.29,0:10:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.73,0:10:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天去買吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.86,0:10:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 去買吧 愈來愈興奮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.54,0:10:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.44,0:10:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小聲點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.34,0:10:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小聲點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.71,0:11:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很普通啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.88,0:11:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實是很普通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.38,0:11:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經來二樓了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.89,0:11:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有聽到什麼聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.52,0:11:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.99,0:11:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像在搗小麥的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.19,0:11:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒聽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.63,0:11:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.34,0:11:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房間也很普通啊 真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.68,0:11:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一號 別亂說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.48,0:11:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真令人懷念啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.82,0:11:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這個的聲音啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說剛剛那個嗎 搗小麥聲是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.52,0:11:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前很流行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.89,0:11:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.69,0:11:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.92,0:11:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房間也是黑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.26,0:11:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣的聲音啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.49,0:11:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不可以說出真名呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.27,0:12:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二號 有時間閒聊不如去找出魔王的弱點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.04,0:12:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是本名…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.88,0:12:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁魔王在泡茶的這個空檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.08,0:12:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.08,0:12:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都行 像日記、照片或詩歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.48,0:12:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.52,0:12:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可痛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.12,0:12:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.32,0:12:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不行的話即使是內衣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.66,0:12:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓各位久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.96,0:12:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花島 剛剛門的那一頭好像有個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.10,0:12:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.17,0:12:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.80,0:12:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.64,0:12:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊是小惠的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.74,0:12:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小惠 別躲著 出來跟大家打招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.05,0:12:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟？\N都被聽到了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.72,0:12:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.55,0:12:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽快地出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.82,0:12:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是小透和亞里莎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.69,0:13:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊的新朋友嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.99,0:13:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.23,0:13:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是正巧念同一所高中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.26,0:13:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也正巧是同一種性別 毫無關係的外人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.53,0:13:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在挖苦我們嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你姊長得一模一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.14,0:13:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒這回事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.94,0:13:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很像 簡直是一個模子印出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.54,0:13:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 小惠…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.25,0:13:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小惠也會發出電波嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.09,0:13:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個我不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.75,0:13:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只會詛咒別人而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.06,0:13:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是被詛咒後還能加倍奉還
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.53,0:13:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一點我倒是挺自豪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.87,0:13:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是不是很奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.37,0:13:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳別說 妳沒資格說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.27,0:13:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會詛咒呢 要怎麼詛咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.91,0:13:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.64,0:13:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要知道那個人的名字 我就可以輕鬆的詛咒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.38,0:13:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.58,0:14:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還不知道妳們叫什麼名字呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.59,0:14:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不能打擾太久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.49,0:14:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點辦完正事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.49,0:14:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如同五月的輕風般迅速離開這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.60,0:14:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.26,0:14:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點採訪 快點走人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.67,0:14:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.43,0:14:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 我好想馬上走呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.97,0:14:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 回想一下我們來這裡的目的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.07,0:14:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛 起碼得把重點問到才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.78,0:14:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問花島同學妳有弱點嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.54,0:14:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種問法太明顯了 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.61,0:14:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然有囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.58,0:14:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.95,0:14:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.39,0:14:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們是草摩由希王子愛好會的會員吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.76,0:14:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們肯定是很不滿草摩由希最近和小透走得很近吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.56,0:14:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們想消除小透吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.23,0:14:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.13,0:14:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻妨礙到妳們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.67,0:14:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們害怕嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.07,0:14:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.27,0:14:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過想找我的弱點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.31,0:14:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種作法也太孩子氣了點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.88,0:15:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太卑鄙了吧 居然用電波來讀我們心裡想的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.52,0:15:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.22,0:15:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.25,0:15:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.99,0:15:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說得一點也沒錯 我們對於魔女…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.96,0:15:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該說對本田透感到非常礙眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.26,0:15:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.03,0:15:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳可以跟本田透說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.00,0:15:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請她跟由希保持點距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.20,0:15:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是他們的自由吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.74,0:15:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.34,0:15:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因妒忌所產生的行為實在很丟人現眼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.51,0:15:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是妒忌呢 我們只是很生氣罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.64,0:15:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛 她以為她是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.04,0:15:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希的事她到底懂多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.78,0:15:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們不也是嗎 妳們懂小透嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.02,0:15:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被愚弄的小透真是可憐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.12,0:15:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像草摩由希那種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.22,0:15:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種人？妳說那種人了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.39,0:15:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎 妳們有聽到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.49,0:15:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是故意說給我們聽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.36,0:15:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫妳們愚弄小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.60,0:15:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳才是呢 把由希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.87,0:15:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在愚弄我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.47,0:15:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳那空洞無神的眼睛非常瞧不起我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.37,0:16:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛是天生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.44,0:16:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 我們是真的喜歡由希 我們愛他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.94,0:16:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本田透的行為有多傷我們的心妳懂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.05,0:16:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表現出一臉只有自己最受由希寵的模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.05,0:16:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷玩弄由希 得寸進尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.22,0:16:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別以為喜歡對方就可以想說什麼就說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.43,0:16:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為喜歡對方就可以為所欲為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.03,0:16:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這種想法最好反省一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.84,0:16:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因妳單方面的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.17,0:16:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,造成對方沉重的負擔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.94,0:16:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還會傷害到對方 這種事千萬不能忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.32,0:16:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尊敬對方的想法 設身處地替對方著想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.62,0:16:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這份心是很重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.26,0:16:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.89,0:16:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不然最後會惹人討厭的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.13,0:16:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.10,0:16:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.16,0:17:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.90,0:17:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,素子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.68,0:17:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請上車 門要關了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.93,0:17:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.36,0:17:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.73,0:17:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳今天不是要打工嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.80,0:17:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.37,0:17:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子什麼時候知道我們名字的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.48,0:17:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是我們在搜房子時嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.61,0:17:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,素子學姐 電波女說要泡茶給我們喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.45,0:17:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.99,0:17:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小南 美緒要強勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.92,0:17:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要用強勢來喝茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.03,0:18:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毒電波會讓人昏睡一星期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.06,0:18:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被詛咒豈不是要睡上一個月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.43,0:18:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我看不只昏睡就能解決啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.93,0:18:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二號 他叫我二號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.20,0:18:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光知道二號是無法詛咒的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.94,0:18:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是走運啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.14,0:18:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是太多事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.85,0:18:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.12,0:18:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也有點妒忌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.42,0:18:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺上小透像被草摩他們給搶走似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.53,0:18:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得有點寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.43,0:18:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.80,0:18:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須學習設身處地替對方著想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.54,0:18:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.98,0:18:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說不可以太任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.02,0:19:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能像那四個人那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.49,0:19:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說了"那種人"這句話也傷害到由希了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.89,0:19:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是負面的示範啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.16,0:19:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.43,0:19:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.94,0:19:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在車站碰到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.17,0:19:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小花 木之下她們四人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.74,0:19:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.41,0:19:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了 小透 亞里莎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.28,0:19:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.65,0:19:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 好久不見了 小惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.69,0:19:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透這傢伙好像很擔心妳呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.99,0:19:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙怎麼這麼早就走了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.06,0:19:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.13,0:19:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當妳在乎某人時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.30,0:19:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時會覺得很難過 很寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.28,0:19:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.74,0:20:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種感覺還挺開心的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.92,0:20:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 小惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.12,0:20:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒跟你比賽吃糯米糰了 要不要比啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.79,0:20:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.09,0:20:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幫妳們泡茶 小透要不要吃糯米糰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.53,0:20:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.16,0:20:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.17,0:20:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最大的弱點永遠都是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.94,0:20:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.95,0:20:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.08,0:20:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.85,0:20:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.75,0:20:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天雖然不知不覺溜了 但我絕不會屈服於妳們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.96,0:20:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨妳便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.43,0:20:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒會在三天後奏效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.00,0:20:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花島 難道妳弟弟真的…真的會詛咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.03,0:20:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.20,0:20:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答案三天後就揭曉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.60,0:21:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.77,0:21:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔王 妳是個名符其實的魔王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.88,0:21:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,素子學姐請妳冷靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.58,0:21:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三天後 三天後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.51,0:21:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道在小花家裡發生了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.35,0:21:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事後也都沒人跟我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.45,0:21:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當小花碰到麻煩時 我能為她做些什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.53,0:21:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.43,0:21:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望自己有能力保護自己最珍惜的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.73,0:21:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不該那麼說你 真抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.27,0:21:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實你也吃了不少苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.51,0:21:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 就如同小花她那樣永遠都會在一旁保護我
